Package org.hibernate.engine.spi

Class SessionFactoryDelegatingImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.engine.spi.SessionFactoryDelegatingImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    jakarta.persistence.EntityManagerFactory, Closeable, Serializable, AutoCloseable, Referenceable, Mapping, SessionFactoryImplementor, HibernateEntityManagerFactory, QueryParameterBindingTypeResolver, SqmCreationContext, SessionFactory, SqlAstCreationContext
    public class SessionFactoryDelegatingImpl
extends Object
implements SessionFactoryImplementor, SessionFactory
    Base delegating implementation of the SessionFactory and SessionFactoryImplementor contracts for intended for easier implementation of SessionFactory.
